== irc.perl.org #perlde

+* Anyone who speaks german or wants to learn it, you are welcome
   to join our channel
+* In contrast to topic channels, people just hang around and
   talk about any (perl) topic
+* If you are having a programming problem, just drop your question
   there, and eventually someone will help
+* not much traffic usually. you can change that!

